# IDE Configuration

## JetBrains CLion

CLion allows you to disable their formatting engine to get
setting from CLangFormat:
in `Settings > Editor > Code Style > C/C++`, enable
`Enable ClangFormat support (only for C/C++/ObjectiveC)` checkbox.
